<h2>FTML improvements</h2>

<p>Introduce three different paragraph types:</p>

<ul>
  <li>
    <p>Pure: Only allows for text content</p>
  </li>
</ul>

<ul>
  <li>
    <p>Leaf: Allows for text content with inline styling</p>
  </li>
</ul>

<ul>
  <li>
    <p>Container: Allows list of children which can be any paragraph type</p>
  </li>
</ul>

<p>
  Based on this the action to modify a paragraph type should be the following:
</p>

<ul>
  <li>
    <p>
      If the current paragraph is at the top level: Change the type to the
      requested one.
    </p>
  </li>
</ul>

<ul>
  <li>
    <p>
      If the current paragraph is the sole child of it's parent container:
      Change the parent container's type.
    </p>
  </li>
</ul>

<ul>
  <li>
    <p>
      If other siblings to the current paragraph exist: Only change this
      paragraphs type.
    </p>
  </li>
</ul>

<p>These are our currently supported paragraph types:</p>

